Machamp (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
This article lists each primary appearance of Machamp in the Trading Card Game. For the deck archetype based around Machamp, see Machamp archetype (TCG).
← #0067: Machoke
Pokémon
#0069: Bellsprout →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Machamp (TCG Pocket).

Machamp has been featured on 31 different cards since it debuted in the Base Set of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Machamp cards are normally Fighting-type Stage 2 Pokémon.
